{"tid":1691942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「香港人，反抗」？對唔住，我笑左","createTime":"2019-11-04T00:55:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T09:17:58.000Z","uid":208752,"like":16,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e4013b246ce6004968ffd17e631920db0c6c08df","tid":1691942,"uid":208752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T00:55:50.000Z","msg":"運動持續左差唔多5個月，越黎越多人被捕，越黎越多悲劇發生，香港人根本無乜點進步過，到依家依一刻都剩係識得週末快樂抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n甚至有部份偽民主鬥士，一邊話自己好黃深黃，另一邊連罷食、文宣依啲咁簡單嘅野都無做過，一尾剩係識free ride。<br />\n<br />\n講真，過左咁多個月，我都心死到七七八八。<br />\n<br />\n再唔改變夜晚/週末嘅抗爭模式嘅話，下句口號直接改成「香港人，返工！」算吧啦。<br />\n<br />\n開得post 都預左有人屌我分化，麻煩你Block柒我之前諗清楚我講嘅野係咪正正反映緊依場運動嘅樽頸位啦"},{"pid":"521bc3806feca325634cc137cdce5cbb4d3fe71c","tid":1691942,"uid":322508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T00:57:16.000Z","msg":"絕對讚同 要改變為日常先有用 唔少巴絲都有提出"},{"pid":"2a3427da46bc88cd62689d59ae6da5c053857375","tid":1691942,"uid":1241,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T00:58:46.000Z","msg":"已經灰到七七八八<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申放負"},{"pid":"3b6c73435bf61628b2c7d3ac05839ff29aaa484c","tid":1691942,"uid":208752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T01:01:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"962f6590a055aa493e07f829f447a951d46310fa","tid":1691942,"uid":257368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T01:08:43.000Z","msg":"Plan緊罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有返工既入一入<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkonstrike\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike&d=JjpB%2FqIgFksXGEBY%2BN5axBdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=6ff9feea\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkonstrike</a>"},{"pid":"3ab6283553e11dbf7ea5f6055586f2f7c9c468b2","tid":1691942,"uid":239663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T01:12:15.000Z","msg":"先唔屌星期一至五正常翻工<br />\n<br />\n問題係星期六日抗爭方式停留咗係一個死位到，每次都拉二百個都算，無目標乜都無達成過咁損失先慘。<br />\n<br />\n等人權法通過前做多啲犧牲已經講唔通，美國個邊過唔過到都成問題"},{"pid":"dcad9e099709c0201934beb4998dd147ec6fe0d1","tid":1691942,"uid":208752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T01:20:47.000Z","msg":"入黎放低負皮嘅人方唔方便解釋下，你負皮我係因為我講左個事實出黎，定係我唔可以屌醒人？"},{"pid":"21e739dab298c902397490e5556ef0646afebd3d","tid":1691942,"uid":304516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:32:07.000Z","msg":"啱到駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20eba175f7fef7815b4868055f243bde09173c95","tid":1691942,"uid":208752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:47:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1b3349fbfd129aeeda0c7daa798c928b8158cee6","tid":1691942,"uid":276581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:56:36.000Z","msg":"香港人 返工"},{"pid":"a647800d04dfdb26ec692bcb39f1ee22b194c70d","tid":1691942,"uid":208752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:27:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a2bb832580be10544f462c3b4b05ab08fb99217c","tid":1691942,"uid":208752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T09:04:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"517217ee75948666ce9fd60806e6c2bc67973cf9","tid":1691942,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T09:06:32.000Z","msg":"見撚到班話憎狗 但日日post自己吃喝玩樂既相<br />\n<br />\n示威遊行活動永遠唔撚見人<br />\n<br />\n出面有人就死呀 <br />\n<br />\n你地班仆街仲post 食野玩既相<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n個男仔條命為咗班咁既仆街冇咗 唔撚值呀屌"},{"pid":"a5fb75fe9fbb9b295a602fc26aa3abc3fb705cba","tid":1691942,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T09:11:29.000Z","msg":"而家警甴惡撚到可以共產黨都唔驚，放多d風啦，等大陸d生番人民鬥人民，點解我地唔可以令返佢地人民鬥人民？<br />\n<br />\neg. <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1689332\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1689332</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，到今時今日都冇一隊人拎住中共旗 I love Popo tee 去打狗，已經知道係唔撚識玩<br />\n<br />\n新聞敢播？ 警甴會捉一隊愛國人士？<br />\n<br />\n跟本唔識玩"},{"pid":"6b966e2dbd7a43ac7bc4327